<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.9.10">
<l>kaṇṭukēṭ ṭuṟṟumōntuṇṭuḻalu maiṅkaruvi</l>
<l>kaṇṭaviṉpan terivariya vaḷavillāc ciṟṟiṉpa</l>
<l>moṇṭoṭiyā ṭirumakaḷu nīyumē nilāniṟpak</l>
<l>kaṇṭacatir kaṇṭoḻintē ṉaṭaintēṉuṉ ṟiruvaṭiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The pleasure that is seen by the five senses that roam about seeing, hearing,</l>
<l>feeling, smelling [and] eating is a small pleasure without measure, difficult to be clear about.</l>
<l>While she with bright bracelets, the lady Śrī and you keep standing,</l>
I <l>have ceased seeing the seen limit. I have attained your sacred feet.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
